Text: Excellent collection! But where's Physicist? That's one of his best, hands down!

The reason I didn't add Physicist is because I don't have it. It's probably my least favorite of all his albums and even Devin himself considers it his worst album to date. If you really want it, I'm sure you can find it somewhere on this site.
So you don't include Physicist, his "worst" album, but you have Biomech in at 192kbps? You're fucking nuts.

This music is free, so shut the fuck up.

Biomech is fucking brilliant. Still one of his best albums, especially seeing as it was his first.

Physicist is god awful. Horrible riffs, shitty lyrics, really vapid songwriting all around. Just, tripe.

tl;dr no you.
Thanks horrace this helps complete my collection.
